name: **Illaunrossalough**
description: Illaunrossalough L904-376 Sheet 44 Large footprint of mud and weedy rocks at LW, low and rough but substantial at HW. This islet is unattractive for the leisure seeker and remote of access. The only easily accessible access pier is 5km to the SW at Flannery Pier L868-354.A pier at L899-383 is private and awkward of approach. A pier at L909-378 is public but down a lengthy twisting boreen. Ungrazed and rough, a place of otters and seals.
